# Investor Relations

# Reliable Energy for Today and Tomorrow

## Corporate Profile

We are a leading provider of reliable, affordable, baseload energy for domestic and international markets. Our expanding and diverse portfolio of assets is positioned to grow in tandem with the evolving demand for diverse energy solutions in the United States and abroad. We are a Master Limited Partnership with over two decades of operational experience trading on the NASDAQ under the ticker symbol “ARLP.”
